# This file is OPTIONAL. By default the app uses Ollama (a local model) for real,
# free results with no key at all. Copy to .env.local only if you want to change
# a provider's settings. .env.local is gitignored — never commit a real key.

# --- Ollama (local model, default provider) ---
# Where the local Ollama server lives. Default shown; usually no need to set it.
# OLLAMA_HOST=http://localhost:11434

# --- Anthropic / Claude (optional) ---
# Set this to enable the Anthropic provider for real Claude results.
# Get a key at https://console.anthropic.com/
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# --- Demo (simulated) ---
# Force simulated outputs regardless of provider (zero-setup hosted demo, or a
# key/Ollama you don't want to actually call). Leave unset for normal use.

